reviewText: Ok I got all of the kicking series they are really great to use when practicing your kicking skills a must have.

I am very disspoined in this. Its cheaply made and very short. I paid $1 for this video and regret wasting my money on it. Im sure the other dvds in the Chinese Kicking series are just as  crappy. Don't waste your money on this product. You will very disappointed as I am.
